Document: VisualShaderNode
Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernode.rst
Summary: Describes the properties and their setters/getters for the VisualShaderNode class in Godot.

Property Descriptions

Property: linked_parent_graph_frame
Type: int
Default: -1
Description: Represents the index of the frame this node is linked to. If set to -1 the node is not linked to any frame.
Setters/Getters:
- void set_frame(value: int)
- int get_frame()

Property: output_port_for_preview
Type: int
Default: -1
Description: Sets the output port index which will be showed for preview. If set to -1 no port will be open for preview.
Setters/Getters:
- void set_output_port_for_preview(value: int)
- int get_output_port_for_preview()
